{{if .visual_result}}
{{if eq .visual_result "pass"}}
### ✅ Consignment Inspection Passed

The visual inspection of the consignment has been completed successfully.

* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`
* **Inspection Date**: {{if .inspection_date}}{{.inspection_date}}{{else}}Recorded{{end}}
* **Result**: 🟢 Pass — Consignment cleared
{{else if eq .visual_result "fail"}}
### 🔴 Consignment Inspection Failed

The visual inspection of the consignment has identified issues. The consignment cannot proceed for a phytosanitary certificate.

* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`
* **Result**: 🔴 Fail — Deficiencies found
{{end}}
{{else if .traderinput.inspection_date}}
### ⏳ Consignment Inspection Scheduled

Your consignment inspection has been scheduled. The PQS officer will attend the consignment site at the agreed time.

* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`
* **Scheduled Date**: {{.traderinput.inspection_date}}
* **Scheduled Time**: {{.traderinput.inspection_time}}
* **On-Site Contact**: {{.traderinput.contact_name}} ({{.traderinput.contact_phone}})

Please ensure the consignment is accessible at the scheduled time.
{{else}}
### 📅 Schedule Your Consignment Inspection

A physical inspection of your consignment is required. Please use the form below to propose an inspection date and time.

* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`

A PQS officer will attend the consignment location at the scheduled time to conduct the inspection.
{{end}}
